  "texts": [
    "This applies unevenly across sequence, structure and function data, which has implications for different tool types.",
    "The rate of generation of these data types is also distributed unevenly across biological agents.",
    "To our knowledge these trends have not been comprehensively publicly assessed.The Centre for Long-Term Resilience & RAND Europe",
    "Villalobos, Pablo, and David Atanasov. 2025.",
    "\"Announcing our Expanded Biology AI Coverage.\""
